    <item>
      <title>大发将于一月份暂停运营并对合作伙伴进行赔偿</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-25/daihatsu-to-suspend-operations-in-january-compensate-partners</link>
      <description><![CDATA[大发汽车公司将在 1 月份停止发货并暂停运营，因为这家丰田汽车公司子公司试图遏制一项调查的影响，该调查显示其大部分车辆没有经过适当的碰撞安全测试。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-25/daihatsu-to-suspend-operations-in-january-compensate-partners</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Dec 2023 06:55:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本央行上田认为积极通胀对政策进程的好处</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-25/boj-ueda-touts-benefits-of-positive-inflation-on-policy-process</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本央行行长上田一夫指出，在正常经济条件下提高利率具有一些积极的潜在影响，同时重申将继续耐心实施货币宽松政策，以追求稳定的通胀。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-25/boj-ueda-touts-benefits-of-positive-inflation-on-policy-process</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Dec 2023 05:49:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国因裸卖空而对法国巴黎银行和汇丰银行罚款 2000 万美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-25/korea-fines-global-banks-record-20-million-for-illegal-naked-short-selling</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据一位知情人士透露，韩国已决定对法国巴黎银行及其国内经纪部门和汇丰控股有限公司处以裸卖空共计 265 亿韩元（2040 万美元）的罚款。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-25/korea-fines-global-banks-record-20-million-for-illegal-naked-short-selling</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Dec 2023 03:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
